    "Use Case: DenseNet architectures are known for their parameter efficiency and feature reuse, making them effective for tasks with limited data or computational resources. 4.",
    "EfficientNetB3 5.",
    "Architecture: EfficientNetB3 is part of the EfficientNet family, employing a compound scaling method to optimize both depth and width of the network.",
    "It consists of 7 convolutional layers followed by a fully connected layer, with 3.1 million trainable parameters. 6.",
